Feature: Update Event
Scenario 1: Update Event Successfully
Given: The user wants to update an event.
Events list contains the event to be updated.
When: The user enters the date and time of the event to be updated.
The system finds the event in the events list.
Then: The system displays the current event information.
The user is prompted to enter new information for the event (bride name, groom name, date, time, number of guests, venue, location, phone).
The system updates the event with the new information.
The system displays the updated event information.
The system confirms that the event was updated successfully.